The '''pols''' and '''[[springar]]''' are [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[folk dances]] in 3/4. They are essentially fast versions of the [[Nordic countries|Nordic]] [[polska (dance)|polska]].<ref>http://www.tcscandinavian.org/aboutdance.html</ref><ref>http://www.austinscandi.org/norwegian.html</ref>

