[[File:Stunt Terry Grant-2.jpg|thumb|upright|Grant performing in 2007]] '''Terry Grant''' is a multiple [[World record|world-record]] holding [[stunt driver]] from the United Kingdom.
==Biography== Grant, born in the United Kingdom, is a [[stunt driver]] who performs at live events around the world.<ref name="AW_2018-07-16"/><ref name="SC"/> He is the holder of multiple [[World record|world-records]], including having executed the highest [[Vertical loop|loop-the-loop]] in a car, the fastest two-wheel mile, the furthest [[barrel roll]] jump, the most [[Doughnut (driving)|doughnuts]] standing on the roof of a car, and the highest number of doughnuts in 100 seconds.<ref name="GWR_2017-07-20"/><ref name="SC"/>
